headline: Bemis Flushes the Competition With Nationwide Launch of Bidet Toilet Seat at The Home Depot
summary: SHEBOYGAN FALLS, Wis., July 22, 2025--Bemis, a leading manufacturer of quality, innovative bathroom products, today announced the nationwide launch of its Renew Wash electric bidet toilet seat, now available in The Home Depot stores and online. Priced at $199, the Renew Wash brings a premium set of features — including unlimited warm water, a heated seat, a warm air dryer and a built-in night light — into an affordable, sleek design for everyday consumers.
